      <title>汤姆·布雷迪计划以 1.5 亿美元的价格出售“亿万富翁地堡”豪宅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/tom-brady-looks-to-sell-billionaire-bunker-mansion-in-florida</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汤姆·布雷迪正在考虑出售其位于佛罗里达州印第安溪岛的豪宅，该岛是被称为“亿万富翁堡垒”的专属飞地，自杰夫·贝佐斯到来后，这里的房产价值飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/tom-brady-looks-to-sell-billionaire-bunker-mansion-in-florida</guid>
