    <item>
      <title>加密货币首富 CZ 将风险投资公司转变为巨型家族理财室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/crypto-s-richest-man-cz-zhao-turns-binance-labs-into-family-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赵长鹏（音）几个月前刚出狱，凭借加密货币的持续上涨，他的财富达到了 700 亿美元，他正在将币安控股有限公司（Binance Holdings Ltd.）的前风险投资部门转变为家族理财室。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/crypto-s-richest-man-cz-zhao-turns-binance-labs-into-family-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>百万富翁纷纷离开之际，里夫斯将放宽英国非居民规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/reeves-to-relax-uk-non-dom-rules-amid-millionaires-leaving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，她将放宽对英国富裕外国人（即“非英国居民”）税制的一些改变，因担心工党政府的政策会迫使百万富翁离开英国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/reeves-to-relax-uk-non-dom-rules-amid-millionaires-leaving</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 12:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
